Mother's Day Brunch - Vineyard closed to the public from 11-2
events.body:
**THE VINEYARD WILL BE CLOSED TO THE PUBLIC FROM 11-2 DURING THE MOTHER'S DAY BRUNCH. THIS IS A TICKETED, 21+ EVENT.**

Buffet-style brunch, live music and a wine tasting (or 1 glass of wine) are included in your ticket price. Brunch will be served from 11-1:00. Live music by [Mike & Leah](https://www.facebook.com/jmichaelleach) is from 11-1:30. There are no table reservations for this event. Just grab a plate and sit wherever you like! The vineyard opens back up to the public at 2.

Memorial Day Celebration
events.body:
Finish out Memorial Day weekend right at Nasketucket Bay Vineyardwith great live music by [Mike and Adlie](https://www.facebook.com/adlieandmikeacoustic) and some summer comfort foods from the legendary [Oxford Creamery](https://www.facebook.com/TheOxfordCreamery) food truck: the Oxcart! Choose your meal option in the add-on section of your Eventbrite ticket purchase and have your Oxcart lunch pack waiting for you when you arrive! **THIS IS A 21+ EVENT.**

**Lunch pack options:**

* Mini lobster roll, slaw, fries, clam cakes and ice cream for $26
* 2 Cheeseburger sliders, fries, clam cakes and ice cream for $20
* Veggie burger, fries and ice cream for $19
* Grilled cheese, fries and ice cream for $19

Father's Day Brunch
events.body:
THIS IS A 21+ EVENT. TICKETS MUST BE PURCHASED IN ADVANCE.

Treat Dad to something special this year with a Father's Day Brunch at Nasketucket Bay Vineyard. Tickets include a buffet-style BBQ brunch, a wine tasting (or a glass of wine) and a very special live music performance by Corey Smaller, flying in all the way from Utah just for this event! You won't want to miss this! Table reservations are not available for this event, just grab a plate and sit wherever you'd like! Brunch will be served from 11:30 - 1. Live music is from 11-1:30. The vineyard will be closed to the public during this event and will open back up to the public at 2 pm.

Maker Session - Burlap Wreath
events.body: Sip some wine, nosh on snacks from our farm store and let your creative side flourish during this Maker Session at Nasketucket Bay Vineyard. Jamie from [J&P Wreaths](https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61555438873147) will be here to instruct this group class on how to make a burlap wreath. Take home your masterpeice to show off to your friends! Tickets are $60 for this event and can be purchased through Eventbrite by clicking [HERE](https://www.eventbrite.com/e/maker-session-burlap-wreath-tickets-884208981867)
